sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Giao diện frontend
    participant Chat as ChatController
    participant AF as AiFallbackService
    participant RasaSvc as RasaChatService
    participant Rasa as Rasa Server
    participant Act as Action Server
    participant Internal as Internal API
    participant DB as SQL Server

    FE->>Chat: POST /api/Chat/{sessionId}/messages
    Chat->>AF: NormalizeContextAsync(...)
    AF-->>Chat: message đã chuẩn hóa
    Chat->>RasaSvc: ParseIntentAsync(...)
    RasaSvc-->>Chat: intent đã phân tích
    Chat->>RasaSvc: SendMessageAsync(...)
    RasaSvc->>Rasa: REST webhook
    Rasa->>Act: custom action nếu cần
    Act->>Internal: Gọi API với X-Rasa-Token
    Internal->>DB: Đọc hoặc ghi dữ liệu
    DB-->>Internal: kết quả
    Internal-->>Act: JSON response
    Act-->>Rasa: payload trợ lý ảo
    Rasa-->>RasaSvc: reply list
    RasaSvc-->>Chat: phản hồi trợ lý ảo
    Chat->>DB: Lưu chat messages
    Chat-->>FE: ChatThreadDto
